分，总在盒子里乱窜。你的职责就是从盒子里蹦出的怪物中找出那些不同的怪物。可爱的画面，俏皮的音效，优美的音乐，十分挑战玩家的的找茬功力。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">竞赛规则：</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 本次活动分排名奖和新浪微博晒成绩奖</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 玩家通过进入《怪物工厂》，寻找在每个关卡中不一样的怪物，过关后获得游戏分数，挑战更多的关卡可以获得更多游戏分数！挑战你找茬功力的极限吧！游戏结束后，系统会把你的成绩上传到PLAY+游戏中心。把所获得的成绩进行截图并通过新浪微博进行发布可参与幸运抽奖 。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">活动时间：</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 4月27至5月10日</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">【奖品规则】：</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 一、排名奖</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 1.获得分数最高的头20名的玩家获得以下奖励：</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 第一名：7800毫安移动电源</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 第二名、第三名：蓝牙耳机</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 第四名至第七名：蓝牙无线鼠标</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 第八至第十一名：gameloft限量衬衫一件</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 第十二至第十五名：100元移动话费</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 第十六至二十名：说客泡泡毛公仔（小码）&nbsp;</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">二、新浪微 博发晒成绩奖：</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 凡是通过新浪微 博发晒成绩的玩家均有机会获得说客耳机一份或50元话费</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">活动结束进入成绩统计阶段，我们将从所有发布过成绩的玩家中抽取15名玩家，其中5人获得话费50元，其余10人获得说客耳机一份。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">移动MM安卓客户端参与活动方式：</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 编辑短信 “ MM ” 发送至 “ 10658800 ”根据回复短信的提示安装 MM 客户端，在客户端搜索框输入“怪物工厂（完美免费版）”进行搜索下载。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">活动地址： http://dev.10086.cn/cmdn/bbs/thread-74570-1-1.html&nbsp;</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">游戏WAP下载地址：http://a.10086.cn/pams2/s/s.do?gId=300002468751&amp;c=172&amp;j=l&amp;blockId=17360&amp;p=72&amp;src=5610007016</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">游戏WWW下载地址：http://mm.10086.cn/portal/web/channel.do?channelId=3310006322&amp;url=http://mm.10086.cn/1009/300002468751.html</span></span></p>','','',1,1,1,1335542400,1423124860,1423809632),(65,'game','索乐游戏发布《松饼骑士》官方中文版','','','索乐游戏与全球知名手机游戏开发商Angry Mob Games公司合作，全球首发《松饼骑士》安卓官方中文版！这是继《游击队员鲍勃》之后，两大巨头再度携手，给大家带来全新的游戏体验。','<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 索乐游戏与全球知名手机游戏开发商Angry Mob Games公司合作，全球首发《松饼骑士》安卓官方中文版！这是继《游击队员鲍勃》之后，两大巨头再度携手，给大家带来全新的游戏体验。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150205/14231249412260.jpg\" _src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150205/14231249412260.jpg\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 《松饼骑士》是一款面向全平台智能手机系统的休闲益智类游戏，带有超炫的视觉效果和大量的童话人物。每一位人物都有独特技能，随着玩家的成长这些技能会不断加强。操作按键也只有四个按键：左、右、攻击、跳跃。玩家可以操作游戏人物，或躲避或攻击不断向下的松饼守卫者，尽可能多的收集松饼。收集松饼和攻击守卫者都有经验值，获取松饼获得15点经验，击败敌人获得1点经验。经验值可以升级。每次升级有一个升级点。升级点可以用来升级人物本领或学习公共技能。故事讲述了一个小男孩在返回魔法松饼森林的路上被施了奇怪的魔咒：只要碰到松饼，就会变成不同的角色。魔女答应他只要他得到所有的松饼，就把他变回来。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">游戏特色</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ★童话式游戏画面</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 绝妙的2.5D 画面，充分利用最新集成引擎特色。从神奇的手画艺术品中，发觉多姿多彩的迷人世界。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; ★ 可爱至极</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 扮演拥有独特的攻击技能18个不同角色。用独特的方式包围龙，乌龟，狼人，幽灵，蝙蝠，妖精和其他可爱毛茸茸动物。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ★ 游戏难度设置</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 升级，解锁新人物以及提升能力。六个技能能够在追寻小松饼时给你带来附加能量。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; ★史诗级Boss战</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 最后你要击败邪恶的火山王来证明你的能力。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ★跨平台多人游戏</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 在iphone，ipod，ipad或安卓设备上挑战玩友，进行激烈直接的多人比赛。游戏适用于NVIDIA Tegra设备。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 索乐游戏是中国领先的手机游戏发行商和游戏运营商，是中国最国际化的手机游戏公司。索乐公司成立于2005年，总部位于上海。2010年上海世博会官方授权手机游戏开发公司和2010年广州亚运会亚运手机游戏开发公司正是索乐游戏。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 索乐公司拥有200款品牌和精品手机游戏内容，覆盖Android, IOS, Java, Windows Phone, Symbian, Brew等各种移动平台。通过遍布全球的200多家合作伙伴，索乐的游戏发行网络已经覆盖了亚洲，美洲，欧洲，非洲等40余国国家的100家电信运营商，包括中国移动，中国联通，Verizon, AT&amp;T，Vodafone，T-mobile，NTT Docomo以及SKT等全球主流运营商。此外，索乐公司与诺基亚，摩托罗拉，索尼爱立信，华为，中兴，联想等全球及中国主流终端厂商合作，年游戏安装终端数量达千万台以上。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 随着《松饼骑士》官方中文版正式发布，必将给索乐游戏的品牌榜上增加一个新的名字。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 索乐游戏，精彩无限！索乐公司的理念是，为游戏玩家创造乐趣，为合作伙伴创造价值，为中国游戏赢得国际声誉。作为中国手机游戏行业的先锋，索乐正在不断探索与进步。我们真诚期待与您的共赢合作，共赴全球移动互联网产业和移动游戏崛起的盛宴！</span></span></p>','','',1,1,1,1335628800,1423124964,1423809607),(66,'game','N多杯“游戏家”网游争霸赛','','','N多杯“游戏家”网游争霸赛','<p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体