nbsp; &nbsp; 本款游戏结合《愤怒的小鸟》与《植物大战僵尸》全新独特的弹射塔防玩法，简单上手却难于精通。这里游戏将蔬菜武装成斗士，各种技能整装待发，“豌豆”三珠连发，“辣椒”喷射火焰等，超过六十关的故事环节，超越极限的的挑战模式，各种道具和博彩的关卡，各种技能和道具的组合搭配，给你带来全方位多角度的游戏体验！蔬菜升级，BOSS升级，新颖绚丽而独一无二！</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">画面精致 清新丰富</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 从游戏的画面来看，可以用无可挑剔来形容，完美的配色效果，柔畅的线条笔锋，精致细腻小清新的2D游戏画面，毫不逊色3D的效果，让你眼前一亮！小清新的画面风格依旧保持画面内容的丰富程度，树荫碧云蓝天，与可爱的蔬菜相得益彰，蓬荜生辉！</span></span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></span></span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19p