span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 在这盛夏八月，有高温，有阵雨，还有浓浓散不开的爱意。在“东方情人节”七夕到来之际，索乐游戏旗下休闲弹射塔防第一手游《燃烧的蔬菜2》将重磅推出“微博活动，七夕节！呼唤你心中的男神”节日活动。只要转发“燃烧的蔬菜”新浪微博中的活动即可轻松参与，赢取大礼。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 燃烧的蔬菜2美术小组还特意为七夕节日制作了一个特殊表情，蔬菜粉丝们只需在燃烧的蔬菜官方微信中点开表情菜单即可下载本次节日特制表情了，届时夏季限量蔬菜周边都将逐一送上，为广大菜心粉丝们在东方情人节日馈赠佳偶增添筹码。即刻，就让我们共同携手微博活动与爱走天涯。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">燃烧的蔬菜2官方新浪微博：http://e.weibo.com/growaway/profile</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">燃烧的蔬菜2官方腾讯微博：http://e.t.qq.com/socoshanghai?preview</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0