height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">2、奖励物品均为绑定；</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">3、同一角色只能获得一次奖励，以玩家最高排名奖励发放；</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">4、只有参与跟帖才能获得该活动奖励，没有参与跟帖无法获得活动奖励；</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">5、活动奖励将在活动结束后三个工作日内发放；</span></span></p>','','',1,1,1,1376928000,1423196250,1423196250),(95,'game','《燃烧的蔬菜2》新版本月光花园抢先评测','','','索乐游戏原创的手游大作《燃烧的蔬菜2》新版本已于近日上线，与所有蔬菜玩家见面。除了增加2个全新蔬菜伙伴之外，这次版本更新中还将增加一个游戏关卡和全新入侵生物及BOSS来增加游戏难度。小编已于第一时间体验了蔬菜2的新版内容，大家一起来先睹为快吧。','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232001691450.jpg\" _src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232001691450.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 索乐游戏原创的手游大作《燃烧的蔬菜2》新版本已于近日上线，与所有蔬菜玩家见面。除了增加2个全新蔬菜伙伴之外，这次版本更新中还将增加一个游戏关卡和全新入侵生物及BOSS来增加游戏难度。小编已于第一时间体验了蔬菜2的新版内容，大家一起来先睹为快吧。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232001996796.jpg\" _src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232001996796.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">1、魔法水滴、怪物碰到后获得防护罩一个，攻击一次后消除。（小怪物体验感受：被保护的感觉无比安逸。）</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">2、魔法旋窝、射出的蔬菜经过产生魔法转换，类似于传送门的效果，除抛射系不会触发效果。（蔬菜小伙伴体验感受：传说中的次元之门谁敢挡我！）</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">3、迷雾系统、遮挡玩家的视线，将可能完全遮挡住画面哟，你需要等迷雾缓慢的飘散。（小编体验后抱怨：能再坑点不，只能瞎猫碰死耗子乱打一气了）</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">4、新伙伴椰菜宝宝属于抛物线射击型角色，在爆炸后能分裂成三个小花花的说，还可以再次爆炸造成伤害这就是所谓的溅射伤害。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232002245498.jpg\" _src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232002245498.jpg\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">5、新伙伴小笋尖的能力完全贯穿伤害加上眩晕效果将成为你强超级蔬菜伙伴，防止入侵之必备蔬菜！</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 最后在月影花园里有一只全身绿油油，眉毛似鹿角，双眼囧囧有神的强壮头目正带着手下喽啰们前来挑战，蔬菜村的菜心们是否与小伙伴们准备好了？关底的神秘大BOSS能否抵挡的住？全新关卡、全新BOSS值得你前来挑战！</span></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232002516728.jpg\" _src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232002516728.jpg\"/></span></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 《燃烧的蔬菜2》还有更多萌趣、新鲜特别的玩法等待着你自己去探索！菜心伙伴们！记得要晒出你们的战绩哟！</span></span></span></span></p>','','',1,1,1,1377532800,1423200290,1423808716),(96,'game','《燃烧的蔬菜2》电脑模拟正版来袭!','','','本次索乐游戏与Bluestacks（美国）合作联手，推出了PC模拟手机游戏《燃烧的蔬菜2》正式版本。《燃烧的蔬菜2》是一款萌系弹射式塔防休闲游戏，该游戏集成了策略、塔防、卡片组合等特色于一身，讲述了各种蔬菜与各种怪兽之间的斗争。','<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 本次索乐游戏与Bluestacks（美国）合作联手，推出了PC模拟手机游戏《燃烧的蔬菜2》正式版本。《燃烧的蔬菜2》是一款萌系弹射式塔防休闲游戏，该游戏集成了策略、塔防、卡片组合等特色于一身，讲述了各种蔬菜与各种怪兽之间的斗争。玩法轻松简单，可采用多种策略、相互克制来抵御怪兽的来袭，让玩家有自由发挥的空间，简单爽快。玩家通过多种蔬菜朋友的的组合，已最大火力，快速有效的将怪兽消灭在入侵的道路上。PC版本中保留了如：迷雾，新小游戏， 新BOSS的开启，增加了游戏的挑战性和乐趣。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232003421764.jpg\" _src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232003421764.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 索乐游戏与BlueStacks的合作，把索乐旗下所有Android游戏带到个人电脑市场,无需对游戏做任何修改。 BlueStacks的App Player软件通过专利的千层糕 （LayerCake）的虚拟化技术，能使索乐的Android游戏神奇地运在个人电脑上。 “燃烧蔬菜2是中国最流行的弹射式塔防休闲游戏之一”索乐游戏CEO沈烨说 “我们一直想从移动终端扩大到个人电脑上，BlueStacks是理想的合作伙伴，提供帮助我们在个人电脑市场增长的最好的技术”。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; “我们与索乐游戏在中国的合作是非常令人兴奋的。”BlueStacks的全球销售和业务开发的高级副总裁阿普库马尔说，“我们AppPlayer软件在中国有数以百万计的下载量，并正在迅速增长。 在中国，我们与顶级游戏开发商，应用程序商店和平台供应商合作，把他们的移动游戏和应用程序带到个人电脑市场“。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232003623469.jpg\" _src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232003623469.jpg\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">BlueStacks App Player虚拟器，包括燃烧蔬菜的最新版本可以从本地的BlueStacks网站或索乐游戏网站下载。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">BlueStacks App Player虚拟器下载地址：http://www.bluestacks.cn</span></p>','','',1,1,1,1377705600,1423200394,1423808685),(97,'news','《燃烧的蔬菜2》官网正式上线！','','','《燃烧的蔬菜2》作为索乐游戏的原创手游品牌，今日首度公开了最新官网。《燃烧的蔬菜2》精美、可爱萌系游戏画面，蔬菜伙伴们奋力抵御怪物入侵、丰富有趣的小游戏系统，一系列优质游戏特性，让许多蔬菜粉丝爱不释手。','<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 《燃烧的蔬菜2》作为索乐游戏的原创手游品牌，今日首度公开了最新官网。《燃烧的蔬菜2》精美、可爱萌系游戏画面，蔬菜伙伴们奋力抵御怪物入侵、丰富有趣的小游戏系统，一系列优质游戏特性，让许多蔬菜粉丝爱不释手。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/1423200462677.jpg\" _src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/1423200462677.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 而刚刚面世的《燃烧的蔬菜2》官网，在这炎热的夏天，打开蔬菜2官网就有一丝凉意、卖萌可爱的蔬菜角色，简洁明了的操作按钮，详尽的游戏特色、周边、活动介绍，令您在游戏之前，率先体验蔬菜2的文化，在阅览蔬菜2官网的同时还能直接获得额外的礼物，为您的蔬菜之旅带来更多的惊喜。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">　　《燃烧的蔬菜2》中营造了一个蔬菜们保护家园的世界，在怪物不断入侵的生存环境战争中它还能保持一片充满欢乐的家园景象，各种蔬菜伙伴们为了守卫住一片乐土，他们都有着各自独特的技能。但入侵并未因首领被击倒而结束。新的一轮入侵即将来袭，守护一片乐土的职责与造就长久和平的梦想在每个协助蔬菜伙伴的人心中萦绕。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">官网地址：http://www.ranshaodeshucai.com/</span></span></p>','','',1,1,1,1378051200,1423200504,1423805978),(98,'news','祝贺！《燃烧的蔬菜2》荣获2013年小米游戏米粉最佳的单机游戏奖！','','','随着小米游戏周年答谢暨2013米粉最爱颁奖礼圆满落幕，在各奖项水落石出之时，索乐自主研发弹射塔防单机大作《燃烧的蔬菜2》捕获了众多米粉玩家们心，最终荣获最佳单机游戏奖项。','<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 随着小米游戏周年答谢暨2013米粉最爱颁奖礼圆满落幕，在各奖项水落石出之时，索乐自主研发弹射塔防单机大作《燃烧的蔬菜2》捕获了众多米粉玩家们心，最终荣获最佳单机游戏奖项。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 《燃烧的蔬菜2》是一款萌系弹射式塔防休闲游戏，该游戏集成了策略、塔防、卡片组合等特色于一身，讲述了各种蔬菜与各种怪兽之间的斗争。玩法轻松简单，可采用多种策略、相互克制来抵御怪兽的来袭，让玩家有自由发挥的空间，简单爽快。玩家通过多种蔬菜朋友的的组合，已最大火力，快速有效的将怪兽消灭在入侵的道路上。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 在《燃烧的蔬菜2》获奖之后，我们再接再厉研发的IOS版本即将与广大IOS手机用户们见面，敬请期待！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232005904427.jpg\" _src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232005904427.jpg\"/></span></p>','','',1,1,1,1378915200,1423200599,1423805950),(99,'game','《燃烧的蔬菜2》安卓最萌趣的游戏','','','拥有3000W粉丝超高人气的燃烧的蔬菜系列，最新续作《燃烧的蔬菜2》即将登陆ios!《燃烧的蔬菜2》是一款弹射式塔防游戏。勇敢的蔬菜们用自己的身体当武器，利用弹弓弹射出去击倒怪物保卫蔬菜家园！','<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 拥有3000W粉丝超高人气的燃烧的蔬菜系列，最新续作《燃烧的蔬菜2》即将登陆ios!《燃烧的蔬菜2》是一款弹射式塔防游戏。勇敢的蔬菜们用自己的身体当武器，利用弹弓弹射出去击倒怪物保卫蔬菜家园！</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232006316723.jpg\" _src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232006316723.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 《燃烧的蔬菜2》独创蔬菜升级系统，强化蔬菜使攻击更猛烈！百变的进化系统，蔬菜升级后可以进化成第二阶段。在一代基础上增加了全新的故事、全新系统、更多种类的蔬菜、强大的怪物家族以及丰富的小游戏。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; GameLook报道：《燃烧的蔬菜2》7月4日安卓首发上线后蔬菜系列游戏日收入已逾45万元！</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232006933738.jpg\" _src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232006933738.jpg\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">《燃烧的蔬菜》系列荣获奖项：</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">2011年-2012年（上）中国最佳移动应用产品评选：</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">最佳手机游戏奖 燃烧的蔬菜</span></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232007207333.jpg\" _src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232007207333.jpg\"/></span></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">2013年5月</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; 