normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/1423200776702.jpg\" _src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/1423200776702.jpg\"/></span></span></span></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></span></span></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 上海索乐软件有限公司是中国领先的手机游戏发行商和游戏运营商，是中国最国际化的手机游戏公司。索乐公司成立于2005年，总部位于上海。索乐是2010年上海世博会官方授权手机游戏开发公司和2010年广州亚运会亚运手机游戏开发公司。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 索乐游戏，精彩无限！索乐公司的理念是，为游戏玩家创造乐趣，为合作伙伴创造价值，为中国游戏赢得国际声誉。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>','','',1,1,1,1379347200,1423200810,1423808664),(100,'game','手游空战王者《空战英豪1945》首发评测','','','《空战英豪1945》一款空战迷必备游戏，让玩家体验到那战火纷飞的天空战场无限魅力。复古空战，激情风暴席卷不停，经典再现！','<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 《空战英豪1945》一款空战迷必备游戏，让玩家体验到那战火纷飞的天空战场无限魅力。复古空战，激情风暴席卷不停，经典再现！</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 《空战英豪1945》是一款经典纵版飞行射击游戏，在AppStor以及Google Play上取得了非常大的成功，长达数年的时间内霸占了全球各个国家空战射击游戏榜的榜首，全球下载已超千万次！受到了广泛玩家的喜爱，成功演绎复古空战风！</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 飞行射击类游戏非常的多，经典的《沙罗曼蛇》，《雷电》，《1914》等等，在当时可以说受到许多玩家的喜欢。特别是一些游戏好手，常常可以控制着飞机在空中辗转腾挪，躲避敌人攻击的同时，将对手统统消灭，有时甚至一滴血都不掉，小编看着是各种羡慕嫉妒恨啊~!今天为大家带来的这款《空战英豪1945》是一款非常不错的飞行射击类游戏，可玩性非常高，快来随小编一起体验一下吧！&nbsp;</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">画面上：</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 作为一款飞行射击游戏，游戏的画面是很重要的。《空战英豪1945》采用的是Unity3D引擎打造，游戏风格就是在很大的程度是还原了二战的战场的真实性。区别其他的飞行射击游戏那种高科技超华丽的动漫系风格，还原真正的战场打造真正的铁血战争。高低空飞行不同的飞行姿态，炸弹在水面和地面上爆炸的效果不同，复古场景犹如回到了战火纷飞的战争年代。复古的战机、精心雕琢的炮弹、效果绚丽的爆炸场景将战争的空战场景映射得一览无遗！</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232008445112.jpg\" _src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232008445112.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: medium; text-align: left;\">（爆炸溅起的水花和陆地战场）</span><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">游戏音乐：</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 游戏的背景音乐整体上采用了重音效果的音乐，激情浑厚的声音加上子弹射击时的声让准军事迷的小编欲罢不能，整个游戏音乐让你振奋、让你热血澎湃，飞机飞过时那整耳欲聋的引擎轰鸣声和炸弹落下时那爆破声还有炸弹落水时那溅起的水花的声音都表现的十分的优异，随着时而紧张时而轻松的音效一起来感受战场的硝烟。感觉就是在一边玩游戏一边享受游戏带给你的震撼。带着你的思绪回到了那战火纷飞的战场。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">操作控制：</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 飞行射击类游戏对于操控有着很高的要求，小编个人最喜欢的还是街机的摇杆，操作起来非常的直接而且有感觉。而作为一款大屏手机游戏，《空战英豪1945》提供了触屏操控模式也非常的简单方便，通过手指在屏幕上的滑动就能实现战机左右腾挪上下翻滚，轻轻的滑动就完成了一系列的高难动作。从左到右从上到下随意的滑动没有丝毫的卡顿，操作感很好，稍稍的适应下就能翱翔与天际了。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232008709924.jpg\" _src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232008709924.jpg\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: medium; text-align: left;\">（各种翻转的动作效果）</span><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">游戏体验：</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 游戏的剧情当然是驾驶战机战斗在辽阔的天空中，在游戏中玩家作为二战中的一员参与到战争中来，来完成每一关的任务消灭更多的敌人。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">游戏关卡丰富，多个关卡供玩家挑战，58种不同造型的敌人。提供3架不同火力的战机供玩家选择，并能解锁各类成就，耐玩性超级棒，通过一根手指触屏你就能操作战机穿梭于枪林弹雨，飞机会随着运动方向呈现出行云流水般的飞行动作，而丰富给力的火力种类更能使你如虎添翼，将敌军各种兵器消灭殆尽！在你炸爆敌机后，游戏会出现各式各样的奖励，包括金币、弹药升级及额外防御等！赚到的金币可在商店购买生命、装备等让你过足空战瘾！关卡中的各种桥梁建筑，还能通过投掷炸弹将其摧毁，令游戏的真实感更为提升。</span></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232008816750.jpg\" _src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232008816750.jpg\"/></span></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: medium; text-align: left;\">（商城中升级之后的强悍火力）</span><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">游戏玩法：</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 游戏的系统设置也是非常的到位。首先，主要任务是打通不同的关卡，玩家在游戏中通过收集金币来升级飞机的护甲、子弹威力和其他的如巡航导弹等等。另外，你也可以购买金币，然后在商店里购买各种道具来提升飞机的各种性能，让你在天空中变得更加的强大。支线任务就是完成各种的成就，完成不同的成就就会有不同的奖励。</span></span></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></span></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232008987613.jpg\" _src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232008987613.jpg\"/></span></span></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: medium; text-align: left;\">（游戏商城和游戏成就的截图）</span><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">游戏场景：</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 游戏场景设定精美，在广阔的土地上，蔚蓝的海面上还有绵延的群山之间展开的战斗，让你既体验了游戏的乐趣又能很好感受空战带来的激情。山河湖海，平原大陆各种不同的战斗场景一定带给你视觉上的冲击让你不会感到审美疲劳。&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></span></span></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232009198636.jpg\" _src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232009198636.jpg\"/></span></span></span></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: medium; text-align: left;\">（各种不同的战斗场景）</span><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 《空战英豪1945》带你进入逼真的空战世界，一起演绎复古空战风，一享空战的绝世快感！快来成为战斗的一员，一起感受那战火纷飞的年代带给我们的无限的激情。让我们的心一起随风而飞。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>','','',1,1,1,1379347200,1423201009,1423808560),(101,'game','《燃烧的蔬菜2》登入QQ游戏大厅','','','近日，由索乐游戏的单机手游《燃烧的蔬菜2》最新版本月光花园已强势登入腾讯手机QQ游戏平台中，这也是QQ游戏大厅将接入最近3款重磅游戏的其中之一，在另外2款<《植物大战僵尸2和腾讯自己的QQ欢乐升级后,《燃烧的蔬菜2》也将在QQ游戏手机平台备受关注。','<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 近日，由索乐游戏的单机手游《燃烧的蔬菜2》最新版本月光花园已强势登入腾讯手机QQ游戏平台中，这也是QQ游戏大厅将接入最近3款重磅游戏的其中之一，在另外2款&lt;《植物大战僵尸2和腾讯自己的qq欢乐升级后,《燃烧的蔬菜2》也将在qq游戏手机平台备受关注。&lt; span=&quot;&quot;&gt;<!--《植物大战僵尸2和腾讯自己的qq欢乐升级后,《燃烧的蔬菜2》也将在qq游戏手机平台备受关注。<--></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232010441630.jpg\" _src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232010441630.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 燃烧的蔬菜是索乐游戏原创的品牌。是一款弹射式塔防休闲游戏，该游戏集成了策略、塔防、卡片组合等特色于一身，游戏的故事主要讲述了各种蔬菜与各种怪兽之间斗争。游戏的玩法较为开放，可采用多种策略、相互克制来抵御怪兽的来袭，最大限度的让玩家自由发挥，简单爽快。特别适合各类喜爱休闲和萌系游戏的玩家。在游戏中，玩家通过多种蔬菜朋友的的组合，达到最大火力，快速有效的将怪兽消灭在入侵的道路上，不同的敌人不同的玩法，加之迷雾， BOSS等等陆续的出现，增加了游戏的挑战性和乐趣。&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;业内人士分析，《燃烧的蔬菜2》将可能延续之前在其他平台的劲爆下载量。同时《燃烧的蔬菜2》极有可能已同样的方式在手机QQ游戏大厅的“聚乐”模式下，让玩家尝试在线上线下数据互通游戏乐趣。实现玩家在彼此聚会时相互晒自己的最新过关记录，当然这一模式也将成为同学聚会互动最好工具。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232010618371.jpg\" _src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232010618371.jpg\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 《燃烧的蔬菜2》月光花园版本不仅增加了游戏的趣味性，在游戏画质上也大幅提升。无论如何，还没玩过《燃烧的蔬菜2》的小伙伴们赶快去下载吧！</span></span></span></p>','','',1,1,1,1380470400,1423201094,1423808538),(102,'game','《燃烧的蔬菜2》国庆送豪礼下载赢手机','','','借着国庆的来临，《燃烧的蔬菜2》与QQ手机平台携手推出了国庆佳节送豪礼活动，让广大玩家在此节日里享受休假的同时更，还能收获一份超级豪礼。立刻下载《燃烧的蔬菜2》，就有机会赢取三星Note2手机大礼，有没有心动了呢？让我们赶快看看活动介绍吧！','<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19px; white-space: 