！《燃烧的蔬菜2》正式推出IOS版本！','','','《燃烧的蔬菜2》IOS版本已于近日正式登陆app store！这是一款拥有亿万粉丝，安卓市场收入破千万的明星级产品！《燃烧的蔬菜2》独创蔬菜升级系统，强化蔬菜使其攻击更加猛烈！百变进化系统，蔬菜升级后华丽变身。','<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;《燃烧的蔬菜2》IOS版本已于近日正式登陆app store！这是一款拥有亿万粉丝，安卓市场收入破千万的明星级产品！《燃烧的蔬菜2》独创蔬菜升级系统，强化蔬菜使其攻击更加猛烈！百变进化系统，蔬菜升级后华丽变身。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 另外在一代基础上增加了崭新的故事内容、全新UI系统以及更多的关卡。游戏中还提供了很多人气小游戏作为附加游戏模式，不管是喜欢何种类型的玩家，都可在《燃烧的蔬菜2》中找到属于自己的乐趣。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232015268630.jpg\" _src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232015268630.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">特点：</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">1、全新故事，全新游戏场景：</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">原创故事背景，蔬菜们的冒险旅程，幽默欢乐不枯燥。根据新的故事背景制作了全新的游戏场景，从海底大战到荒岛冒险，带你畅游神秘的蔬菜大陆！</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">2：蔬菜升级，模样进化：</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">全新的蔬菜升级系统，升级蔬菜可以增强攻击力。蔬菜升级后，会呈现崭新模样！更萌更帅！</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">3：全新BOSS，战斗难度火爆升级：</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">游戏新增“首领猛犸”和“独眼章鱼王”，BOSS技能多变，火力凶猛，带给玩家全新的挑战！</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">4：崭新绚丽小游戏,更多休闲玩法：</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">游戏除了主要的塔防玩法，在玩家疲惫的时候还准备了轻松休闲的小游戏。只要三个以上同样的蔬菜聚拢在一起，他们就能欢快地翻滚了。简单的玩法即能获得大量的金币又能获得精美游戏道具奖励！</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">5:新增伙伴，战斗更多样：</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">新伙伴: 小萝卜头；呆萌搞怪，鬼点子多。强力贯穿，穿透射击直线排列在一起的怪物。胆小菇；胆小可爱，威力强大。弹出后埋伏在目标地，待怪物靠近连续释放闪电强力攻击。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">赶快下载《燃烧的蔬菜2》体验最萌趣的冒险吧！</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">官方下载地址：https://itunes.apple.com/cn/app/ran-shao-shu-cai2-ran-shao/id710369217?mt=8</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">《燃烧的蔬菜2》官方网站：www.ranshaodeshucai.com</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">《燃烧的蔬菜2》官方微信：socoshanghai</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">《燃烧的蔬菜2》官方微博：http://weibo.com/growaway</span></span></p>','','',1,1,1,1383062400,1423201557,1423808463),(105,'news','GameLook：延伸生命力《燃烧的蔬菜》开启品牌化','','','GameLook报道 / 11月08日，“索乐《燃烧的蔬菜》文化产品发布会”在苏州举行。众多媒体、运营商、平台、厂商、以及动漫衍生产业链公司代表齐聚一堂。','<p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp; &nbsp; GameLook报道 / 11月08日，“索乐《燃烧的蔬菜》文化产品发布会”在苏州举行。众多媒体、运营商、平台、厂商、以及动漫衍生产业链公司代表齐聚一堂。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 发布会现场嘉宾+玩家人数gamelook目测超过500、晚宴差不多有20桌，且在苏州金鸡湖畔五星级酒店招待，可见此次活动规模之大、花费之巨，堪称今年手游行业单一公司产品发布会人数之最的活动，然而，主角却是一款单机手机游戏：《燃烧的蔬菜》。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 一向被网游产品压几头的单机手游今年开始掷地有声，捕鱼算一家、蔬菜算一家，但作为游戏业一向类似农林牧副渔的单机游戏，《燃烧的蔬菜》却做了很多手机网游不愿做、不敢做的事：全产业链的品牌化，将在音乐、桌游、漫画、表情、周边等领域进行文化产品开发，一系列的线下产品，为互联网、出版行业准备的漫画系列已开始散播，索乐希望长久把《燃烧的蔬菜》这个品牌经营下去。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 要这么干一定要有足够的财力，品牌从来都是做长线、短期难以看到立竿见影的效果，要把这一摊子的线下产品、不赚钱的动漫画产品坚持下去，需要财力更需要持久的耐心，但一旦做成品牌，则会为企业带来滚滚的土豪金。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 在发布会现场，索乐CEO沈烨提到《燃烧的蔬菜》系列自去年8月诞生一年以来的成绩，截止今年9月底累计用户规模已达7000万，月下载量增长在千万左右，年底累计用户将突破1亿，收入表现更是惊人，在单机游戏所依赖的运营商计费上，《燃烧的蔬菜》占了差不多三大运营商每月这块5%的流水，系列更是突破了千万月收入，单日最高收入峰值破百万，收入表现超出了很多人的想象。在这个成绩背后，无法忽略的是索乐对这款游戏的投入，80人的团队为蔬菜日夜操劳，单机游戏有这么大的团队支撑，能想象么？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 品牌化，一句话总结就是“叫好”要远超“叫座”才行，首先你要用一定的用户基础，有核心的喜欢你的粉丝存在，然后把赚的钱拿一部分出来温养用户，呈现品牌的丰富性，人性化，最终让用户记住、并被认可。一个成功的品牌一定具有用户喜爱的地方，而为了加速这种喜欢的程度、体现你的好并让用户看到，可能是做十件事才能让用户感受到一件，因为你不知道哪件才是对用户最有效的，是真的被认可而不是自作矫情，所以做品牌累，你无法很精确的去衡量，更多凭的是对用户的了解，甚至是灵机一动，而在品牌化的道路上投入可以是无底洞。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 《燃烧的蔬菜》是一款有着品牌化基础的单机游戏，代表12星座的蔬菜角色十分可爱，玩法也非常轻度化，老少咸宜，因此获得了庞大的用户。索乐给蔬菜提炼的品牌关键词是：快乐、健康，这也代表着现实社会的潜在诉求。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 而在gamelook看来，索乐这一系列的品牌化操作，目的显而易见:为这款高收入单机游戏延长生命线，同时通过品牌化尝试文化行业内的跨产业链，用索乐CEO沈烨的话说，做品牌就是在提高竞争的门槛，但可惜的是，有这样想法的国产手游产品并不多。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 也许，单机游戏相比重度产品来说，更易于品牌化，也许让重度游戏从游戏这个点上实现品牌很难，但衡量一个产业是否成功、最终认的还是诞生多少强大的品牌，希望我们这个年轻的行业的从业者们早日醒悟，路走的人多了就成了真正的大道，希望业内的一线企业能勇于尝试。</span></p>','','',1,1,1,1384272000,1423201733,1423800663),(106,'news','新浪：索乐将《燃烧的蔬菜》打造成文化品牌','','','2013年11月8日，“索乐《燃烧的蔬菜》文化产品发布会”在苏州金鸡湖凯宾斯基酒店举行。发布会中，索乐首席执行官沈烨表示，公司将把旗下手游产品《燃烧的蔬菜》打造成全新的热门文化品牌。','<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 2013年11月8日，“索乐《燃烧的蔬菜》文化产品发布会”在苏州金鸡湖凯宾斯基酒店举行。发布会中，索乐首席执行官沈烨表示，公司将把旗下手游产品《燃烧的蔬菜》打造成全新的热门文化品牌。</span><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232018224396.jpg\" _src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232018224396.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; text-align: -webkit-center; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">《燃烧的蔬菜》邮票</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232018526279.jpg\" _src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232018526279.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; text-align: -webkit-center; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">《燃烧的蔬菜》桌游和明信片</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; text-align: -webkit-center; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/142320187390.jpg\" _src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/142320187390.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; text-align: -webkit-center; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; text-align: -webkit-center; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">《燃烧的蔬菜》漫画产品</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; text-align: -webkit-center; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; text-align: -webkit-center; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; text-align: -webkit-center; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; text-align: -webkit-center; white-space: normal;\"></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 《燃烧的蔬菜》是由索乐游戏开发的休闲弹射式塔防手游，游戏自2012年8月推出，第二作也已于2013年7月上线。据索乐公布的数字显示，截止至9月底，《燃烧的蔬菜》用户规模已达7000万，而随着IOS版和一系列新版本的更新，索乐预计该游戏的用户规模将在今年年底突破1亿大关。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">　　凭借庞大的用户群，索乐将以中国版“愤怒的小鸟”为目标，扩展游戏的品牌影响力和产品链，为手游《燃烧的蔬菜》打造出完整的文化品牌。除了今年9月由滚石磅礴音乐旗下艺人柳丁创作并演唱的《燃烧的蔬菜》主题曲以外，索乐CEO沈烨还在发布会上公布了一系列该手游的文化产品，例如桌游、漫画、表情、周边等诸多内容。为了制造出文化品牌效应，索乐将在未来与电信运营商、知名媒体、互联网平台、出版社、杂志社、文创等公司进行合作，通过打造一系列产品，为《燃烧的蔬菜》激发出更多文化价值。同时，索乐还计划将《燃烧的蔬菜》文化产品出口到东亚、东南亚市场，进一步增强该品牌的影响力。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">　　发布会中，索乐首次向外界公开了《燃烧的蔬菜》桌游、明信片、邮票等周边，并计划在未来继续推出更多的文化产品，将《燃烧的蔬菜》打造成中国手游的热门文化品牌。</span></p>','','',1,1,1,1384272000,1423201916,1423800620),(107,'game','《燃烧的蔬菜2》IOS版11月8日火爆限免！','','','在这美好的季节有好的东西就一定要和大家一起分享。《燃烧的蔬菜2》自IOS正式发布以来深受玩家喜爱！本次《燃烧的蔬菜2》为了感谢广大玩家的支持！将定于11月8日进行为期三天的限时免费！','<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 在这美好的季节有好的东西就一定要和大家一起分享。《燃烧的蔬菜2》自IOS正式发布以来深受玩家喜爱！本次《燃烧的蔬菜2》为了感谢广大玩家的支持！将定于11月8日进行为期三天的限时免费！</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 史上最萌游戏《燃烧的蔬菜2》独创的蔬菜升级系统，强化蔬菜使其攻击更加猛烈！百变的进化系统，蔬菜升级后可以华丽变身。让你一次弹的痛快，一次燃烧的彻底。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 另外在一代基础上增加了全新的故事、全新系统、全新的关卡。更多种类的蔬菜、强大的怪物家族以及玩法丰富多彩的小游戏。让你一次玩个够，一次萌到底。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 密切关注《燃烧的蔬菜2》官方微信、微博即可参与本次限免活动！更有机会赢取罗技iPad无线蓝牙键盘盖、手机话费以及蔬菜2公仔等精美奖品！限时3天！亲们抓紧哟！</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232019839609.jpg\" _src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232019839609.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">《燃烧的蔬菜2》官方网站：www.ranshaodeshucai.com</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">《燃烧的蔬菜2》官方微信：socoshanghai</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">《燃烧的蔬菜2》官方微博：http://weibo.com/growaway</span></span></p>','','',1,1,1,1384444800,1423202008,1423808437),(108,'news','索乐打造中国原创国民级游戏和热门文化品牌','','','索乐打造中国原创国民级游戏和热门文化品牌\r\n--《燃烧的蔬菜》文化产品发布会隆重召开','<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 索乐打造中国原创国民级游戏和热门文化品牌</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">--《燃烧的蔬菜》文化产品发布会隆重召开</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2013年11月08日，“索乐《燃烧的蔬菜》文化产品发布会”在苏州金鸡湖凯宾斯基酒店隆重举行。来自国内外的众多知名媒体、电信运营商、互联网巨头、游戏厂商、动漫业界领军人物、出版社、杂志社、文创公司等聚集一堂，共同见证上海索乐软件有限公司旗下原创游戏品牌《燃烧的蔬菜》正式进军更广泛大文化领域。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232024527672.jpg\" _src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232024527672.jpg\" style=\"width: 688.0952379703522px; height: 403.0952379703522px;\"/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 《燃烧的蔬菜》品牌定位为“欢乐、健康”，该游戏是全球首个以蔬菜为主角的“蔬菜家族”游戏，并开创了“弹射式塔防”游戏玩法。《燃烧的蔬菜》手机游戏自2012年8月推出以来，得到玩家及行业人士的广泛盛赞，被广大网友誉为中国版“愤怒的小鸟”。自2013年7月第二代游戏首发上线以来，用户规模加速增长，截止9月底累计用户规模已达7000万。预计随着IOS版上线、天空之城版本更新，以及新年版等一系列版本的推出后，蔬菜系列游戏用户规模2013年底将突破1亿。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2013年初以来，在广大蔬菜粉丝建议下，索乐公司开始探索将《燃烧的蔬菜》品牌在音乐、桌游、漫画、表情、周边等领域进行文化产品开发。2013年9月，由滚石磅礴音乐旗下艺人柳丁创作并演唱的歌曲《燃烧的蔬菜》在中国移动无线首发,在酷狗等音乐网站首发上榜推广,一经推出即取得了不俗的榜单成绩，开创音乐及游戏合作的先河,开拓音乐及游戏的跨界营销模式样本。2013年11月，以《燃烧的蔬菜》弹射式塔防娱乐为原形由善见城精心打造衍生的首个非平衡类塔防对抗桌面游戏面世，发布会后，会在大电商平台及大实体连锁集中销售。索乐与杭州友诺合作打造的燃烧的蔬菜系列漫画产品，分别针对幼儿、中小学生和青年女性，将游戏成功漫画化，分别推出《燃烧的蔬菜—十二星座》、《燃烧的蔬菜—失落的大陆》等系列漫画产品，通过《中国漫画》、《少年英雄》杂志连载、出版，并通过QQ新浪等主流互联网渠道专区和移动互联网及社交媒体传播。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 预计未来一年内，《燃烧的蔬菜》品牌将通过旗下各类文化产品广泛传播，影响数亿计的广泛受众。同时，《燃烧的蔬菜》文化产品即将随游戏出口到东亚，东南亚市场，让全球粉丝领略蔬菜文化的魅力。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232021104576.jpg\" _src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232021104576.jpg\" style=\"width: 702.0952379703522px; height: 438.0952379703522px;\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 作为一家创新驱动的移动互联网公司，索乐希望，用互联网的方式去做文化产业。通过游戏、音乐、动漫、桌游、衍生等领域跨界合作，赋予《燃烧的蔬菜》品牌更深厚内涵，创作更多欢乐健康的文化内容，探索文化产业新盈利模式。索乐诚邀各界优秀合作伙伴共同打造原创国民级品牌手机游戏和属于中国人自己的热门文化品牌！</span></span></span></p>','','',1,1,1,1384531200,1423202158,1423800580),(109,'game','3D新体验！《燃烧的蔬菜2》“天空之城”首发上线','','','小番番带领蔬菜伙伴们勇敢的战胜了月光花园的怪物，朝着下一个目标出发！这次他们将飞上天空，面临来自空中敌人的挑战，体验炫酷3D世界！进击“天空之城”！','<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 史上最萌！亿万玩家的最爱《燃烧的蔬菜2》开启神秘全新场景“天空之城”啦！</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 小番番带领蔬菜伙伴们勇敢的战胜了月光花园的怪物，朝着下一个目标出发！这次他们将飞上天空，面临来自空中敌人的挑战，体验炫酷3D世界！进击“天空之城”！</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 天空之城开创新奇独特的全新玩法，3D动感场景设计、萌趣的纸飞机、喵星人财宝雕像、益智好玩的金手指以及憨态可爱的天空战队。更有超萌新蔬菜加入！一场惊险的天空之城大战将要上演，这一次你就是蔬菜们的领导者！</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232038933137.jpg\" _src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232038933137.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">“天空之城”的新玩法：</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 纸飞机：关卡中任意地点刷新纸飞机，纸飞机撞击城墙会造成伤害。 &nbsp;</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">财宝雕像：关卡随机刷新小雕像，击破后会掉落金币或者宝石或怪物。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">电流云：吸收的玩家的子弹，反弹电流子弹，对城墙造成伤害。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">“天空之城”全新机制：</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 金手指：使用后，一定时间内，点击怪物后可以进行滑飞的操作，怪物直接飞出屏幕。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 原地复活：玩家在关卡失败后，可以直接通过支付宝石来复活。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 此次《燃烧的蔬菜2》携手360、百度、91、安智、UC、oppo、联想、小米等国内一线优质渠道同步首发，玩家只需下载游戏，即可参与抽奖。苹果最新iPad Air大奖等你来拿！还有大量的精美周边：蔬菜水杯、蔬菜抱枕、蔬菜公仔以及蔬菜手机壳！赶紧下载游戏赢取iPad Air体验3D场景带来的快感！</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232039234402.jpg\" _src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232039234402.jpg\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 进击3D“天空之城”！带给你全方位3D体验！这一次颠覆传统！更有神秘全新蔬菜等你去解锁！</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">《燃烧的蔬菜2》官方网站：www.ranshaodeshucai.com</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">《燃烧的蔬菜2》官方微信：socoshanghai</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">《燃烧的蔬菜2》官方微博：http://weibo.com/growaway</span></span></span></p>','','',1,1,1,1384790400,1423203977,1423808415),(110,'news','GMGC索乐游戏携《燃烧的蔬菜》获奖','','','备受玩家追捧的弹射塔防策略类游戏《燃烧的蔬菜2》亮相成都第二届全球移动游戏开发者大会。在本次大会中《燃烧的蔬菜2》作为一款持续升温的热点手机单机游戏为玩家带来了自己的品牌形象及周边产品。','<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">备受玩家追捧的弹射塔防策略类游戏《燃烧的蔬菜2》亮相成都第二届全球移动游戏开发者大会。在本次大会中《燃烧的蔬菜2》作为一款持续升温的热点手机单机游戏为玩家带来了自己的品牌形象及周边产品。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/></span></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px;\">燃烧的蔬菜展台人潮涌动</span></div><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232040249819.jpg\" _src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/14232040249819.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">工作人员正在为玩家介绍燃烧的蔬菜游戏及周边</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;f