e=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 第二届GMGDC全球移动游戏开发者大会的最大亮点——“天府奖”，是全球移动游戏行业第一个小金人奖，旨在通过该奖向年度游戏制作人、制作团队和公司颁发一个全球移动游戏业界最高荣誉，也堪称移动游戏业界的“奥斯卡”。</span></span></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></span></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/1423204097672.jpg\" _src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150206/1423204097672.jpg\"/></span></span></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-hei