\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp;简约大气的新品牌办公室</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">首家设立品牌部办公室的手游公司</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 这次的开张仪式充分表现出索乐游戏对于品牌部的重视，飞速发展中的索乐希望通过更加优越的办公环境和办公设备，为之后的品牌推广工作打下更坚实的硬件基础。大气简约的办公室让人眼前一亮。前台立着办公桌上放置的各式各样蔬菜玩偶，墙面上形形色色的蔬菜绘本漫画都有让你有种进入蔬菜空间的感觉。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 有趣的是，这里还有一些特殊的“小伙伴”，这些“清洁机器人”墙上爬的，地上跑的随处可见，也为新办公室增添了不少科技感。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 办公室的休闲区域内也设有免费的饮料与零食提供给员工。另外，“新鲜血液”的注入，也无疑是“员工福利”的又一体现。在经过一番招贤纳士后，这次索乐吸收了一批无论是能力还是素质都非常出众的员工，巧合得的是其中不乏美女。 公司的男员工都笑称说：“公司这也是变相给我们增加了福利啊，原本一直都男多女少，现在做起事情来也格外有动力啊。”在提高硬件设备之外“注重员工关怀”同样也是索乐的企业文化。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/></span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img src=\"http://www.socogame.com/caches/upload/20140303/1393824266_319702.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp;“燃烧的蔬菜”定制蛋糕</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img src=\"http://www.socogame.com/caches/upload/20140303/1393824291_026581.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">公司新进的美女员工</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">为什么要做“燃烧的蔬菜”品牌</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 当被问起索乐对“燃烧的蔬菜”在今后有何规划时，索乐CEO沈烨表示：“我们要成为比小米更年轻的品牌，目标是做90，00后最喜爱的文化品牌”</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 经过2年的传播，燃烧的蔬菜系列已累积1亿的游戏用户，月新增用户1千万。欢乐健康的产品理念，也通过各类文化产品（漫画，桌游，表情等）进行传播，让孩子们充满童趣，想象力，正义感。与传统行业不同之处在于，索乐是用互联网精神做文化品牌，更多互动，好玩的元素穿插在其中。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/></span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img src=\"http://www.socogame.com/caches/upload/20140303/1393824351_923076.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">索乐游戏CEO沈烨和蔬菜公仔合影</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">燃烧的蔬菜文化产品布局</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2013年11月索乐在苏州举办了文化产品发布会，吸引了上百家媒体的关注，据悉2014年最新一代的蔬菜游戏也已进入研发的最后阶段，在不久的未来即将上线与广大玩家见面。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 燃烧的蔬菜漫画“失落的大陆”与四格漫画已在《少年英雄》、《中国漫画》、《我们爱科学》等多家知名漫画杂志连载。可爱逗趣的表情系列也登陆搜狗表情。更有豪华阵容打造的《燃烧的蔬菜》动画片的制作也在筹备中。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/></span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img src=\"http://www.socogame.com/caches/upload/20140303/1393824319_273491.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">索乐游戏CEO沈烨畅谈14年新计划</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">索乐游戏集团14年的新产品</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 经八年的发展，目前拥有六家控股、参股公司的索乐集团。从事手机单机、手机网游、网页游戏、电视游戏的研发运营<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 据悉，2014年，索乐游戏将陆续推出《燃烧的蔬菜》社交版本，中国原创Unity3D ARPG 单机大作《恶魔之城》，由国内顶尖体育策略游戏团队历时二年多，千万打造的跨平台游戏《辉煌足球》，回合制手机网游《武侠2》，以及数款ARPG手机网游，品牌规划化，打造出索乐出品，必是精品的口号，我们一起来期待吧。</span></p>','','',1,1,1,1393776000,1423206990,1423799903),(123,'news','GMGC索乐春季新游发布会，三款S级重磅产品亮相','','','2014 GMGC大会首日，索乐游戏在国家会议中心召开索乐春季新游发布会，索乐CEO沈烨代表公司隆重发布三款不同类型的S级新游产品- 即蔬菜系列新一代产品“燃烧的蔬菜社交版“，重磅足球策略游戏“辉煌足球”和中国原创3D RPG大作“恶魔之城。”','<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 2014 GMGC大会首日，索乐游戏在国家会议中心召开索乐春季新游发布会，索乐CEO沈烨代表公司隆重发布三款不同类型的S级新游产品- 即蔬菜系列新一代产品“燃烧的蔬菜社交版“，重磅足球策略游戏“辉煌足球”和中国原创3D RPG大作“恶魔之城。”&nbsp;</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">　　索乐原创的国民级热门休闲游戏“燃烧的蔬菜”系列累计用户已突破1亿，其”欢乐、健康“定位，获得众多忠实蔬菜粉丝。历时一年多研发，”燃烧的蔬菜“最新一代产品 - ”燃烧的蔬菜社交版“即将于今年正式推出。“燃烧的蔬菜社交版“是蔬菜系列的创新产品，游戏采用全新的蔬菜弹射式塔防玩法结合卡牌元素；全新的任务和新玩法；按照社交化设计，有众多的好友交互元素，蔬菜乐园中玩家可以”种菜“，将再度在手机平台掀起全民“摘菜”热潮。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><div align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img src=\"http://www.socogame.com/caches/upload/20140326/1395828274_380526.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></div><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">　　　</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">　　“辉煌足球”是由资深体育策略游戏团队耗资千万，历时两年多，研发的新一代足球策略游戏。辉煌足球在玩法体系，付费深度上，将国产体育策略游戏提高到新的标准。辉煌足球页游版的次日留存率逾30%，日付费率约5%；手游版经小范围封测次日留存率超过60%。预计这款S级产品，将在2014世界杯之年成为最热门体育游戏之一。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><div align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img src=\"http://www.socogame.com/caches/upload/20140326/1395828298_376891.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>　<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></div><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp; &nbsp;“恶魔之城”是一款是堪比好莱坞大片的原创U3D ARPG大作。全新一代暗黑动作角色扮演类手游，带来全新的酷炫华丽战斗体验。厚重的游戏世界观，玩家用自己的力量守护人类文明，挽救天下苍生。可谓为不逊色于欧美大作的国产重磅游戏。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><div align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img src=\"http://www.socogame.com/caches/upload/20140326/1395828314_185062.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></div><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">　　索乐发布会上，还举办了“燃烧的蔬菜动画片签约启动仪式”。索乐携手国产动画金牌导演黄伟明先生，共同打造蔬菜精品动画片。索乐CEO沈烨表示，“燃烧的蔬菜”不仅仅是热门游戏，索乐的目标是，把“燃烧的蔬菜”打造成为”2000后最喜爱的文化品牌”。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img src=\"http://www.socogame.com/caches/upload/20140326/1395828340_862741.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p>','','',1,1,1,1395763200,1423207079,1423799867),(124,'news','GMGC索乐游戏CEO沈烨：今年将推出多款重度游戏','','','3月27日，第三届GMGC全球移动游戏大会在国家会议中心举行，有超过30个国家、300家媒体、800家公司参加，邀请了Google、Facebook、Arm、Intel、腾讯、完美、畅游、金山、蓝港在线、中国联通、中国电信、中国手游、百度91等7000多名公司高层人士出席。索乐游戏CEO沈烨在现场接受了媒体的采访。','<p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none;\"><a href=\"http://www.voiceofgame.com/cn/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2014/03/sy.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none;\"><img alt=\"sy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-11186\" src=\"http://www.voiceofgame.com/cn/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2014/03/sy.jpg\" height=\"330\" width=\"520\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></a></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 3月27日，第三届GMGC全球移动游戏大会在国家会议中心举行，有超过30个国家、300家媒体、800家公司参加，邀请了Google、Facebook、Arm、Intel、腾讯、完美、畅游、金山、蓝港在线、中国联通、中国电信、中国手游、百度91等7000多名公司高层人士出席。索乐游戏CEO沈烨在现场接受了媒体的采访。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">以下是采访实录：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 问：索乐一直坚持做一些休闲类的游戏，我想知道未来的战略当中我们是否还会坚持走这个，还是会进行多元化的发展？</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 沈烨：</strong>我们的定位是一家游戏组合的公司，首先这是第一个定位，这就意味着我们会有不同的团队来做不同的产品，我们在休闲游戏上我们有燃烧蔬菜，就是这款产品有一个多用户，然后每月千万次的用户量，同时我们也有中度和重度的游戏。在昨天我们召开了一个发布会，我们即将推出的有两款比较重度的游戏，一个是足球经纪人的游戏，叫辉煌足球，今年是世界杯年，我们会有一款历时两年研发的大型体育策略游戏，另一方面我们有一款由3DARP级的一款国产精品游戏，叫龙魔之城，我们也刚发布，且4月份将要上线。所以我们是一家轻度、中度、重度组合的公司。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 问：你们当初制定了一个方针，要打造一种文化品牌，我想知道这个方针是如何制定的？</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 沈烨：</strong>这是我们另外一项业务，就是文化品牌业务，产生燃烧蔬菜很多的粉丝，后来我们在想是这样的，我们首先要做一些让大家喜欢的一些文化产品，游戏是其中一种，之后我们在去年下半年开始做了漫画，我们今年漫画的线下的杂志，像我们爱科学，中国漫画这些杂志，他们都在做这个燃烧蔬菜的漫画连载，量上大概是三千多万，当然还有线上的渠道，除此之外昨天跟我们中国的喜洋洋之父黄为民先生举办了签约仪式，由他来担任导演，来做我们燃烧的蔬菜动画片，除此之外还有音乐等等一系列的文化产品，我们会在每个细分领域都让燃烧的蔬菜有内容、有内涵的形成一个燃烧蔬菜的文化品牌。当然文化品牌是一个比较漫长的历程，目前正在探索中。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 问：在3G领域，竞争很激烈，网游也会更多，付费也是一个问题，基于这样一种经验和一些想法，为我们分享下。</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 沈烨：</strong>先回答这个问题，中国市场足够大，轻度、中度和重度的游戏我们觉得都是有机会的。第二个其实用户大量的时间是在单机游戏上，这个大家都看到了。单机游戏的优势是能够形成一个比较庞大的用户量，现在看来全单机肯定存在一定的局限性，而社交化之后会变得好很多，所以大家看到微信平台的一些游戏，它的收入是非常高的。不难理解其原因通过社交化的方式，更进一步提高了留存，这是一个，我们也看到国外像糖果粉粹传奇这种产品，其实它的营收规模都是10亿美金级的。所以我们觉得社交化的单机游戏也是有一个巨大的货币化空间。因为它其实创造一个很大的社会价值，另一方面，单机的产品，我们觉得它比较适合的原因是它的优势是体验下高用户量，它比较适合去做更进一步的文化品牌。前几天有一个电影，极品飞车，就是以前玩的游戏，三天票房就是一个亿，那个电影，所以其实我们看到以后，现在这次会的一个主题，跨界融合，其实像各类文化产品，像电影、电视、游戏、动漫，都是密不可分的。单机游戏其实形成这样一个IP，我们觉得它是可以衍生到其他领域去的，这也是它的优势。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 问：您刚才谈到IP，您之前也说过要做原创游戏，这个可能是原创游戏衍生出来的，我看您之前的新游戏，是否有知名的IP在里面，是否考虑过购买？</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 沈烨：</strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\">其实在09年，10年的时候，我们当时是世博会的官方授权的手机游戏开发公司，那个时候主要还是以快乐女生和西班牙足球为主。在那个时代我们拿过很多IP来做手游，当然那个时候的游戏体验没有现在这么好，也不是主流的行业。在现阶段，我们其实也是在跟品牌的，包括网络小说和其他的一些东西，我们也在积极沟通。因为我们觉得把这种认知度比较高的文化产品拿来改编游戏，还是非常主流的模式。所以我们也在做这方面的探索和合作。</span></span></p>','','',1,1,1,1396195200,1423207199,1423800023),(125,'game','穿越侏罗纪，一起打怪兽 - 《燃烧的蔬菜3恐龙来了》劲爆上线','','','国民级休闲手游大作《燃烧的蔬菜》因其特有蔬菜世界观和独创弹射塔防玩法，赢得了亿万粉丝的喜爱。经过漫长的等待，蔬菜系列的全新一代游戏-《燃烧的蔬菜3恐龙来了》终于要在近期隆重上线了。7月23日，《燃烧的蔬菜3恐龙来了》将在360、百度、腾讯、豌豆荚、安智、UC、91、金山、OPPO、小米、步步高、PPS游戏平台、联想、酷派、金立、搜狗、千尺、4399、华为（排名不分先后）等各大平台首发。','<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;国民级休闲手游大作《燃烧的蔬菜》因其特有蔬菜世界观和独创弹射塔防玩法，赢得了亿万粉丝的喜爱。经过漫长的等待，蔬菜系列的全新一代游戏-《燃烧的蔬菜3恐龙来了》终于要在近期隆重上线了。7月23日，《燃烧的蔬菜3恐龙来了》将在360、百度、腾讯、豌豆荚、安智、UC、91、金山、OPPO、小米、步步高、PPS游戏平台、联想、酷派、金立、搜狗、千尺、4399、华为（排名不分先后）等各大平台首发。</span></span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\";padding: 0px\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\";padding: 0px\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.socogame.com/caches/upload/20140812/1407815903_094673.jpg\" width=\"752\" height=\"467\" style=\";padding: 0px;width: 611px;height: 362px\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px;\"><span style=\";padding: 0px\"><span style=\"padding: 0px;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">　　</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px;\"><span style=\";padding: 0px\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">　　全球的蔬菜粉丝们再度和蔬菜一起开启心跳冒险之旅。在新一波萌宠蔬菜浪潮来临之际，让小编带大家一起看看，蔬菜3有哪些吸引人的全新玩点吧。</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px;\"><span style=\";padding: 0px\"><span style=\"padding: 0px;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">　　　</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px;\"><span style=\";padding: 0px\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;\"><strong style=\";padding: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">全新历险故事&nbsp;燃烧无处不在</span></strong></span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px;\"><span style=\";padding: 0px\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;\"><strong style=\";padding: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></strong></span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px;\"><span style=\";padding: 0px\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">　 《燃烧的蔬菜3恐龙来了》除了延续经典独创的弹射塔防玩法，关卡的巧妙设计，爽快的游戏节奏等特色以外，还添加了小蔬菜们穿越侏罗纪时代的全新动人剧情，令玩家代入感十足。</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px;\"><span style=\";padding: 0px\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\";padding: 0px\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">　　生命在于燃烧，新作中大幅加强的了蔬菜们的属性技能，让“燃烧无处不在”这一游戏主题特色淋漓尽致的体现。战斗中，小蔬菜们的“燃烧”功力越发出神入化，普通蓄力攻击时的激情燃烧，“溅射”技能带来的范围燃烧，“灼烧”技能的持续燃烧，“炎之领域”技能所制造的陷阱式燃烧……团结一致的小蔬菜们，用持之以恒的火攻战术，打退恐龙猛兽，踏上回归家园之路。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"padding: 0px;\"><span style=\";padding: 0px\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;\"></span></span></span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">　　　</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\";padding: 0px\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.socogame.com/caches/upload/20140812/1407815958_509128.jpg\" width=\"639\" height=\"432\" style=\";padding: 0px;width: 611px;height: 363px\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px;\"><span style=\";padding: 0px\"><span style=\"padding: 0px;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">　　　</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px;\"><span style=\";padding: 0px\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;\"><strong style=\";padding: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">核心弹射塔防玩法结合庄园系统&nbsp;&nbsp;蔬菜能力全面大升级</span></strong></span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px;\"><span style=\";padding: 0px\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;\"><strong style=\";padding: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></strong></span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px;\"><span style=\";padding: 0px\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">　 《燃烧的蔬菜3》中，最引人瞩目的莫过于新增的蔬菜庄园系统，不仅让弹弓、城墙都能不断提升等级，而且小蔬菜们也有了一个美丽温馨而又功能强大的庄园作为根据地了，在这里，可以进行培育升级，每日摇奖等有趣的事项，不失为激烈战斗间隙的休闲最佳场所，</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\";padding: 0px\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\";padding: 0px\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.socogame.com/caches/upload/20140812/1407816006_381294.jpg\" width=\"627\" height=\"418\" style=\";padding: 0px;width: 611px;height: 363px\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px;\"><span style=\";padding: 0px\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 在这里，玩家可以根据不同的种子类型，来自由培育出不同的品质蔬菜。而德国哲学家莱布尼茨所说的“世界上没有两片完全相同的叶子”，也在这里得到了变相的印证，游戏中即使是同一种蔬菜，也是会有不同的属性。</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px;\"><span style=\";padding: 0px\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px;\"><span style=\";padding: 0px\"><span style=\"padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"color:#7f7f7f\">　　</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">相信真正的“蔬菜达人”，一定会明白，如何合理的发挥出每一个蔬菜的特长，以便在战斗中取得最佳的效果。本作中新增的“庄园系统”所带来的大幅强化的角色养成要素，也让游戏的战略性、可玩性更为突出。</span></span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px;\"><span style=\";padding: 0px\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16pxcolor:#7f7f7f\">　　在《燃烧的蔬菜》中，金币、宝石变得越发重要，这也让玩家真正开始享受收集的乐趣。金币可以购买道具和种子，以及蔬菜、城墙、弹弓的升级，而宝石可以恢复体力甚至复活，以及加速升级成长，解锁土地等等。为了让自己的蔬菜们变得更强大，玩家必须勤勤恳恳、尽力收集金币和宝石。</span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px;\"><span style=\";padding: 0px\"><span style=\"padding: 0px;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">　　</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px;\"><span style=\";padding: 0px\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;\"><strong style=\";padding: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">全新引擎绚丽画面&nbsp;战斗流畅爽快倍增</span></strong></span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px;\"><span style=\";padding: 0px\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;\"><strong style=\";padding: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></strong></span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px;\"><span style=\";padding: 0px\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">　　原本就清新可爱的画面，在采用全新引擎下得到全面加强，不但一个个蔬菜的角色形象得到更新，更细致的描绘让蔬菜们越发讨人喜爱人。整体游戏场景更为宏大，除了侏罗纪时空，蔬菜庄园等大场景外，周边一草一木的细节元素也更显真是可感。对于战斗时关键招数——弹射，新的一作在重新加强衔接帧数后，动作表现更加自然，操作起来更加流畅，爽快感可以说是成倍提升。</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\";padding: 0px\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\";padding: 0px\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.socogame.com/caches/upload/20140812/1407816058_346187.jpg\" width=\"643\" height=\"443\" style=\";padding: 0px;width: 611px;height: 361px\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; line-height: 19.04762077331543px;\">　</span><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\";padding: 0px\"><span style=\"padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">　　作为国民级热门手游品牌大作，《燃烧的蔬菜3恐龙来了》暑期档即将火爆上线。这个夏天，让我们一起打怪兽吧！劲爆爽快，根本就停不下来！</span></span></span></p>','','',1,1,1,1407772800,1423207322,1423808193),(126,'game','2014 Chinajoy: 索乐空战手游大作 Air Attack 2 重装上阵','','','2014年7月29号，索乐“AIR ATTACK 2“新游发布会在上海飞行家主题园隆重举行。索乐CEO沈烨代表公司发布了即将在夏季档再次雷霆出击的“AIR ATTACK 2”。发布会上，沈烨不仅全方位的介绍了新游戏，同时以颁发奖杯的形式答谢了与索乐合作紧密的渠道和合作商。','<p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;font-size:16px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;2</span><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;color:#7f7f7f;font-size:16px\">014年7月29号，索乐“AIR&nbsp;ATTACK&nbsp;2“新游发布会在上海飞行家主题园隆重举行。索乐CEO沈烨代表公司发布了即将在夏季档再次雷霆出击的“AIR&nbsp;ATTACK&nbsp;2”。发布会上，沈烨不仅全方位的介绍了新游戏，同时以颁发奖杯的形式答谢了与索乐合作紧密的渠道和合作商。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img src=\"http://www.socogame.com/caches/upload/20140812/1407820561_946352.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><div align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp;</span></div><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">Air&nbsp;Attack&nbsp;2雷霆出击</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; AirAttack是由Art&nbsp;in&nbsp;Games推出的基于Unity3D引擎开发的飞行射击游戏，并且获得了Unity3D年度游戏的最高奖项。目前为止，AirAttack凭借其主机级别的画面，大片级的史诗音效和设定完善，充满深度的游戏系统，在Google&nbsp;Play及APP&nbsp;Store的总下载量就已突破1亿次。同时，AirAttack的iOS版本累积在43个国家获得总榜第一，并在61个国家获得游戏榜第一。其中不仅有美国，英国和德国等欧美国家，也包括中国，日本和越南等亚洲国家和地区，可见AirAttack在各国玩家中都广受欢迎。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 在中国，由索乐代理发行的中文版AirAttack——空战英豪，通过与国内厂商与渠道的合作，预装和下载合计也轻松破亿。在经过了长达4年的等待之后，全新的AIR&nbsp;ATTACK&nbsp;2将于今年夏天档雷霆出击。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img src=\"http://www.socogame.com/caches/upload/20140812/1407820577_794230.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><div align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp;</span></div><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;在AIR&nbsp;ATTACK&nbsp;2中玩家可以选择多架战机，全部是来自二战知名战机：有美国海军11：1战绩的“海盗”战机；有评为二战十大战机第一的野马；有太平洋战场击落山本56的“闪电”战机。故事情节完全还原与历史情节，包括诺曼底登陆，太平洋战役以及柏林勃兰登堡门等等。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">更值得一提的是AIR&nbsp;ATTACK2这次的四大特色：</strong></span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">1、更华丽的游戏画面，连建筑爆破砖块落地的效果都能表现出来。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">2、全新射击玩法，不仅可以空战，还可以转换视角空对地射击，甚至可以转化成驾坦克地对地作战。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">3、强力战机对战强大BOSS。每个战机都有升级技能。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">4、前所未见的天气，逼真的画面。这一切都让游戏更具代入感。今年夏天必定又将掀起一股全民“打飞机”的热潮。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">让游戏落地&nbsp;飞行家主题乐园隆重开战</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 考虑到本次发布的“AIR&nbsp;ATTACK2”是一款射击类的空战手游，发布会的举办地选在——飞行家主题乐园，也是索乐对于发布会“用心良苦”的体现。发布会场内一架“波音747”赫然入眼，成为全场最大的亮点。随处可见的“二战元素”，都让每一位来宾都感觉到从游戏角色转换到现实中的刺激感。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img src=\"http://www.socogame.com/caches/upload/20140812/1407820592_038172.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><div align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp;</span></div><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 从游戏到线下，索乐将游戏运营考虑到了最佳的用户体验，不仅仅设计了同款的飞行模型，同时也将会邀请玩家到上海的飞行家乐园，以及全国各主要的城市飞行乐园参观飞机模型、玩街机游戏，甚至体验模拟飞行。通过O2O，让游戏玩家体验飞行的乐趣。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">答谢酒会回馈合作伙伴</span></strong></span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img src=\"http://www.socogame.com/caches/upload/20140812/1407820618_105893.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><div align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp;</span></div><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\