; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;是金子总会发光，好游戏不会被遗忘。据代理商索乐游戏统计，前作《空战英豪1945》在中国市场预装和下载合计已经突破1亿次，夺下了2010年Unity3D年度游戏的最高奖项，IOS版本累积排在43个国家总榜中第一，61个国家获得游戏榜第一，在中国区以外Google Play及APP Store的总下载量更是突破1亿大关。</span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal; top: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;史诗级战争电影大片的画面品质，爽快与细腻兼备的一流操作，完善缜密的系统设定，空战射击游戏大作《空战英豪2》中文版已经将呼啸而来，如此好的游戏怎么能错过？</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\"></span></span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal; top: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>&nbsp;<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.socogame.com/caches/upload/20140924/1411551584_136495.jpg\" width=\"630\" height=\"330\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 615px; height: 330px;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\"></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal; top: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>接触到《空战英豪2》之后的最初印象，莫过于那基于Unity3D引擎所打造出的视觉效果。其中更有来自美国及前苏联的F4U “海盗”、A-51 “野马”、YAK-3M等二战中的著名战机，其建模由顶级三维技术渲染出，不管是从色彩图案还是机身各部位造型方面，都是栩栩如生，真实震撼。在爆炸四起，硝烟滚滚的战场，战机低空掠过盘旋飞行，机枪高速怒射的强大火力，以及战争游戏中罕见的天气变化效果，营造出身临其境的紧张刺激氛围，都会给玩家带来惊心动魄而又酣畅淋漓的游戏体验。</span></span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal; top: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.socogame.com/caches/upload/20140924/1411551643_167492.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"622\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 356px; height: 622px;\"/>&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal; top: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 不夸张的说，《空战英豪2》游戏画面所表现出的“高大上”，比起PS4以及XBOX-one等游戏主机，亦是不遑多让。《空战英豪2》让玩家随时随地爽爆“主机”感觉。</span></span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal; top: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.socogame.com/caches/upload/20140924/1411551670_563491.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal; top: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">当然作为战争射击游戏，手感操作与系统内容也同样成为，在这些方面《空战英豪2》亦为玩家交出满意答卷。游戏中呈现的那些二战中的著名战机不仅造型逼真，而且飞行性能、作战能力等方面同样也是还原度极高，玩家可以操纵它们于枪林弹雨中穿梭，伺机出击，击溃敌方的飞机坦克，并将敌方重要区域摧毁，战斗手感细腻，爽快度与成就感并存。</span></span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal; top: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.socogame.com/caches/upload/20140924/1411551698_219308.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal; top: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">在玩法方面，游戏设定有战役模式、生存模式等多种类型，分别为玩家带来了紧张、痛快、感动等不同的游戏体验。游戏过程中，太平洋战场的波诡云谲、诺曼底登陆的残酷惨烈以及攻克柏林的豪情万丈，被渲染的火爆绚丽，临场感十足。亲身参与这些发生在第二次世界大战的真实战役，绝对是别有一番激爽滋味。</span></span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal; top: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.socogame.com/caches/upload/20140924/1411551730_024978.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal; top: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">空战英豪系列自问世以来，迅速凭借顶尖的画面素质和超强的游戏性，成为最受玩家欢迎的空战射击类游戏代表作品之一, 在世界范围内广受追捧。</span></span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal; top: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;前作曾经的火爆人气和辉煌荣誉，让国内的玩家对于最新一作充满了期待。现作将更加精彩， U3D精品空战大作《空战英豪2》正版激活码，将在通过各大渠道陆续发放，届时会展开定时限量争夺、趣味互动问答等活动，玩家们只要耳聪目明，把握时机，就有机会提前体验到这款U3D精品空战大作所带来的超凡魅力。</span></span></p>','','',1,1,1,1411488000,1423208752,1423808104),(132,'game','惊爆你的眼球！《空战英豪2》视频抢先看！','','','空战大作来了！精致逼真的史诗级画面，足以媲美好莱坞电影大片；二战经典机型英姿重现，火爆畅爽的射击轰炸场面，将彻底点燃你内心热情之火。索乐游戏全球独家首发，精品空战游戏——《空战英豪2》将于9月25日在各大渠道震撼上线。在这之前，就让我们通过游戏视频来抢先感受一下这超强的画面感吧！','<div align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><pre style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; top: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.socogame.com/caches/upload/20140924/1411553006_570483.jpg\" width=\"630\" height=\"330\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 618px; height: 330px;\"/></span></pre></div><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal; top: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal; top: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;