2》等你来战！</span></p>','','',1,1,1,1411488000,1423209091,1423808080),(133,'game','史诗级空战巨作《空战英豪2》今日全球首发','','','缔造弹幕浪漫，再塑空战辉煌！史诗级空战巨作  《空战英豪2》将于9月25日在360、百度、腾讯、豌豆荚、安智、UC、金山、可可游戏、小米、爱奇艺、联想、酷派、金立、搜狗、千尺、4399、华为、VIVO、酷狗、天奕达（排名不分先后）等各大渠道同步震撼首发。一场气势磅礴、紧张刺激空战之旅即将开启！喜爱空战游戏的玩家们可以趁着十一长假穿越到二战战场，驾驶战争史上那些经典战机，尽情体验枪林弹雨中穿梭射击、击破立功的畅爽快感！','<p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal; top: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;缔造弹幕浪漫，再塑空战辉煌！史诗级空战巨作&nbsp; 《空战英豪2》将于9月25日在360、百度、腾讯、豌豆荚、安智、UC、金山、可可游戏、小米、爱奇艺、联想、酷派、金立、搜狗、千尺、4399、华为、VIVO、酷狗、天奕达（排名不分先后）等各大渠道同步震撼首发。一场气势磅礴、紧张刺激空战之旅即将开启！喜爱空战游戏的玩家们可以趁着十一长假穿越到二战战场，驾驶战争史上那些经典战机，尽情体验枪林弹雨中穿梭射击、击破立功的畅爽快感！<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal; top: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150212/14237193342331.jpg\" _src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150212/14237193342331.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal; top: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\"><strong>荣耀人气 历史传承&nbsp; 尽显大作气质</strong><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;《空战英豪2》英文名为《AirAttack2》，由Art in Games制作，索乐游戏全球独家代理首发。游戏基于Unity3D引擎开发，拥有足以媲美PS4等次世代游戏主机的画面素质，再加上劲爆凌厉的音效、丰富多彩的内容，完善缜密、极具的游戏系统，虽是手游却尽显大作气质。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal; top: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 游戏第一作问世后，迅速在全世界范围内赢得耀眼的荣誉和火爆的人气。iOS版本累积在43个国家获得总榜第一，并在61个国家获得游戏榜第一，其中不仅有美国，英国和德国等欧美国家，也包括中国，日本和越南等亚洲国家和地区。在2010年，《空战英豪》在国内还获得了Unity3D年度游戏的最高奖项，这无疑是对于游戏受欢迎程度的又一肯定。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal; top: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\"><br/></span></span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; top: 0px;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana\"><span style=\"line-height: 19.046875px;\"><img src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150212/14237193681952.jpg\" _src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150212/14237193681952.jpg\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana\"><span style=\"line-height: 19.046875px;\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal; top: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\"><strong>顶级绚丽画面&nbsp; 战争大片氛围&nbsp;</strong><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 系列开山之作所具备的巨大的吸引力，已令地球人无法阻挡。在即将上线的第二作《空战英豪2》中，越发精彩的游戏体验，更是让人玩到High处，不忍释手。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal; top: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 《空战英豪2》在画面视觉方面再度下足功夫，轰炸此起彼伏，高射机枪疯狂射击，硝烟浓烈，弹幕遮天，就连建筑爆破砖块落地的效果都能表现出来，再加上前所未有的真实的天气变化效果，呈现出犹如战争史诗大片一般的“高大上”场面，让人完全沉浸到那种激烈残酷的战斗氛围中。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal; top: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\"><br/></span></span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; top: 0px;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana\"><span style=\"line-height: 19.046875px;\"><img src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150212/14237193823559.jpg\" _src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150212/14237193823559.jpg\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana\"><span style=\"line-height: 19.046875px;\"><br/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal; top: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\"><strong>亲手操控经典战机 战场建功</strong><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 游戏内容方面，《空战英豪2》也精心做出全面的更新。玩家可以选择多架二战中的著名战机进行作战，其中就包括了有美国海军11：1战绩的“海盗”战机，被评为二战十大战机第一的野马以及在太平洋战场击落山本56的“闪电”战机等等。在三维建模精美渲染下，这些著名战机不仅造型被还原的真实可感，而且作战能力、特长优势也在战斗中展露无疑，玩家可以通过自己的操作，将他们的优势发挥到极致，从而赢得满满的成就感。<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal; top: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\"><br/></span></span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal; top: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150212/14237193989981.jpg\" _src=\"http://socogame.xtaff.net/cache/upload/images/20150212/14237193989981.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal; top: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\"><strong>丰富游戏模式 感受历史 挑战极限</strong><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 在《空战英豪2》的战役模式中收录了诺曼底登陆，太平洋战役以及柏林勃兰登堡门等等二战中著名的战役事件，生存模式中则包含了无穷无尽的极限挑战。玩家既可以亲自穿越到历史情境中，体验战火纷飞的惨烈，操纵战机谱写历史；也可以来到刺激紧张的生存模式，凭借判断与操作，缔造新的王牌飞行员纪录。丰富多彩的玩法，让游戏的可玩性、耐玩度大幅提升。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal; top: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;《空战英豪2》一到，真正的空战王者降临！次世代主机级别的绚丽画面，穿越到二战战场改写历史，痛快淋漓、欲罢不能的空战射击，战争史诗电影级的手游，你还在等什么，快来下载吧。</span></span></p>','','',1,1,1,1411574400,1423210388,1423822837),(134,'game','《燃烧的蔬菜3》7日更新游戏主角 农场、战队即将再添新丁','','','欢乐蔬菜对决呆萌恐龙，前所未见的弹射塔防新玩法，蔬菜农场缺啥种啥，Fever燃烧模式爽快爆棚,这就是即将更新的《燃烧的蔬菜3》，赶快加入蔬菜3的队伍，让我们一起开始愉快的玩耍吧!','<p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp; &nbsp;欢乐蔬菜对决呆萌恐龙，前所未见的弹射塔防新玩法，蔬菜农场缺啥种啥，Fever燃烧模式爽快爆棚,这就是即将更新的《燃烧的蔬菜3》，赶快加入蔬菜3的队伍，让我们一起开始愉快的玩耍吧!</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.socogame.com/caches/upload/20141106/1415245242_254763.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\"><br/></span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Meiryo, Verdana; line-height: 19.04762077331543px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;font-size:16px;color:#7f7f7f\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&